---
// A2 #740 — /onboarding consolidated into the single /workspace cockpit.
// The former standalone page rendered static, localStorage-backed steps that
// were not derived from get_my_onboarding (misleading: a promoted member saw
// the same 8 "pending" steps). The canonical onboarding/pre-onboarding
// checklists now live in /workspace. Redirect (302, query string preserved).
const qs = Astro.url.search || '';
return Astro.redirect('/workspace' + qs, 302);
